            "type": "text",
            "text": "Conditional prompting selects "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "the next prompt or branch",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " based on classifier output, tool results, or rules — adding if/else logic to agent flows without full ReAct autonomy."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "What it is"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Router prompt returns intent enum; orchestrator switches templates. Example: billing → refund prompt; technical → troubleshooting prompt."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Why it matters"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Specialized prompts outperform one-size-fits-all on narrow branches while keeping overall system understandable."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Implementation"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "codeBlock",
        "attrs": {
          "language": "python"
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "route = classify intent\nif route == \"billing\":\n    response = run_prompt(BILLING_TEMPLATE, state)\nelif route == \"technical\":\n    response = run_prompt(TECH_TEMPLATE, state)"
          }
        ]
      },
